00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,020
Yantang.

291
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:14,119
Madam.

292
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:16,100
Master has been inside for long.

293
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:20,900
Leave us for now.

294
00:20:21,210 --> 00:20:22,420
- Yes, Madam.
- Yes, Madam.

295
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:23,980
Yantang.

296
