00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,060
Yantang.

314
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:11,180
Yantang.

315
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,500
Here. Take the medicine.

316
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:30,060
Yantang.

317
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:33,740
I'm Ms. Longevity.

318
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,580
Yantang.

